    <!-- Add-to-home explainer -->
    <string name="add_to_home_title">Adding to your home screen</string>
    <string name="add_to_home_body">Your phone\'s launcher decides how widgets get placed, and some skins — including MIUI and HyperOS on Xiaomi, Redmi and Poco phones — drop the widget in without drawing it, so it looks like nothing happened.\n\nIf the widget appears blank or missing: press and hold that empty spot on your home screen, tap <b>Edit</b>, and your collage will appear.\n\nThis is the launcher\'s behaviour, not something the app can override.</string>
